content: Looking for someone interested in creating a logo design for a new IT/Geekery franchise.Think of best buy but with ma and pa running it , used and more categories.They sell , Desktops,Components, miners, server, mac's , switches, PC accessories, 3D Printers , Drones , security cameras, radios, VR Stuff, game consoles, programming,install and repair services.Basically anything that branches off the nerd tree of Geekery.The logo of should incorporate symbols or images related to the technology industry, such as computer parts, circuit boards, or 3D printers. The use of bold and modern font styles with a monochromatic or a contrasting color scheme.The theme will be a programming ,Anon, in code we trust ,cyberpunk vibe. PM me for more details.
